Two interesting points about Djokovic's latest statement...
Firstly, you have to admire the linguistic gymnastics required to desperately avoid using the words deport or deportation.  Secondly, you have to wonder why Novax believes his co-operation is required for the deportation to go ahead.  He REALLY believes the Australian government need his permission before they drag him, kicking and screaming, to his Emirates Airlines Super-Spreader flight back home.
